snippet.title: Aero Fighters (1P + 2P teamwork) gameplay and ending
snippet.description:
before my brother had accident, whenever we go to bowling center, we played Aero Fighters.
We usually beat 1st loop with 4 credits.

My brother used ninja Hien (ninja beam!)
I used idol singer Mao Mao (time stop)
